description:
A mobile suit made by the http://anidb.net/ch132071 [Jeturk company] as the previous generation to the http://anidb.net/ch126082 [Dilanza]. http://anidb.net/ch124443 [Shaddiq] provides these to the http://anidb.net/ch131851 [Dawn of Fold] in order to cast suspicion on the Jeturk company during the attack on Plant Quetta.
Source: Official page
name: MD-0021 Desultor
